-- Language: en_US
insert or replace into EnglishText
    (Tag,                                                     Text)
values
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_COLLEGE_DESCRIPTION",                 "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat land adjacent to a Campus district with a Library.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+100% Campus district adjacency bonuses in this City. Established [ICON_Governor] Governor in this city provide +4% [ICON_Science] Science for each Promotion earned, including the first."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_COLLEGE_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",        "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat land adjacent to a Campus district with a Library.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+100% Campus district adjacency bonuses in this City. Established [ICON_Governor] Governor in this city provide +4% [ICON_Science] Science for each Promotion earned, including the first."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_NATIONALEPIC_DESCRIPTION",            "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built adjacent to a Theater Square with an Art Museum or an Archaeological Museum.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+20% [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person points in this city. For every [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person earned, provide +4 yield equal to that [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person's district type.([ICON_Greatgeneral] Great Generals earned provide +4 [ICON_Production] Production. [ICON_Greatadmiral] Great Admirals earned provide +4 [ICON_Food] Food.)"),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_NATIONALEPIC_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",   "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built adjacent to a Theater Square with an Art Museum or an Archaeological Museum.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]+20% [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person points in this city. For every [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person earned, provide +4 yield equal to that [ICON_GreatPerson] Great Person's district type.([ICON_Greatgeneral] Great Generals earned provide +4 [ICON_Production] Production. [ICON_Greatadmiral] Great Admirals earned provide +4 [ICON_Food] Food.)"),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_CITADEL_DESCRIPTION",                 "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Requires that you are at War with other Civilizations. Must be built adjacent to an Encampment district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Provides the same defensive bonuses as the Fort improvement. Grant Walls and Medieval Walls in this City. Promoting a unit does not end that unit's turn. +4 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength for all military units in your territory. All Encampment districts, buildings in Encampment districts and Fort improvements provide +2 [ICON_Production] Production and +2 [ICON_Culture] Culture. Fort improvements provide [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism from [ICON_CULTURE] Culture after researching Flight."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_CITADEL_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",        "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Requires that you are at War with other Civilizations[ENDCOLOR]. Must be built adjacent to an Encampment district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Provides the same defensive bonuses as the Fort improvement. Grant Walls and Medieval Walls in this City. Promoting a unit does not end that unit's turn. +4 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength for all military units in your territory. All Encampment districts, buildings in Encampment districts and Fort improvements provide +2 [ICON_Production] Production and +2 [ICON_Culture] Culture. Fort improvements provide [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism from [ICON_CULTURE] Culture after researching Flight."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_TEMPLE_DESCRIPTION",                  "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Requires that you must have founded a Religion with at least 5 Cities following it. Must be built adjacent to a Holy Site district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]For each Worship building constructed, all your Cities spread Religion with +20% pressure and +10% range. These effects can stack up to 5 times. +1 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture from each city following your Religion."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_TEMPLE_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",         "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Requires that you must have founded a Religion with at least 5 Cities following it.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built adjacent to a Holy Site district.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]For each Worship building constructed, all your Cities spread Religion with +20% pressure and +10% range. These effects can stack up to 5 times. +1 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture from each city following your Religion."),
    
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_THEMEPARK_DESCRIPTION",               "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Requires 4 Entertainment Complex or Waterpark districts to have been built in your empire. Must be built on a flat tile adjacent to an Entertainment Complex district. District built on Breathtaking tiles provide [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism from adjacency bonuses. Wonders provide +300% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Entertainment Complex or Water Park.  Pastures and Camps provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Zoo. Fishing Boats provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Aquarium."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_THEMEPARK_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",      "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Requires 4 Entertainment Complex or Waterpark districts to have been built in your empire.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on a flat tile adjacent to an Entertainment Complex district. District built on Breathtaking tiles provide [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism from adjacency bonuses. Wonders provide +300% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Entertainment Complex or Water Park.  Pastures and Camps provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Zoo. Fishing Boats provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism in Cities having Aquarium."),

    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_IRONWORKS_DESCRIPTION",               "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Improve 4 Strategic Resources in your empire. Must be built on a land tile next to an Industrial Zone district and an [ICON_IRON] Iron resource. All Cities within 8 tiles of the Ironworks receive +3 [ICON_PRODUCTION] production for every type of Strategic Resource properly improved in this City."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WONDER_CL_IRONWORKS_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",      "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Improve 4 Strategic Resources in your empire.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on a land tile next to an Industrial Zone district and an [ICON_IRON] Iron resource. All Cities within 8 tiles of the Ironworks receive +3 [ICON_PRODUCTION] production for every type of Strategic Resource properly improved in this City."),

    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_DESCRIPTION",                    "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes. Must be built on land tile adjacent to an Commercial Hub. Commercial Hub of this city receive +100% adjacency bonus.
    Banks provide +2 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. Stock Exchanges provide +4 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",           "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on land tile adjacent to an Commercial Hub. Commercial Hub of this city receive +100% adjacency bonus. Banks provide +2 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. Stock Exchanges provide +4 [ICON_Gold] Gold to [ICON_TradeRoute] International Trade Routes originated from the city. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_CORP_DESCRIPTION",               "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes. Must be built on land tile adjacent to an Commercial Hub. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Your Corporations provide +200% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. [ICON_GreatWork_Product] Products provide double yields in Cities with a Stock Exchange. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),
    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_FINANCE_CORP_DESCRIPTION_INTERNAL",      "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. [COLOR:Red]To unlock: Maintain 8 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes.[ENDCOLOR] Must be built on land tile adjacent to an Commercial Hub. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Your Corporations provide +200% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. [ICON_GreatWork_Product] Products provide double yields in Cities with a Stock Exchange. [ICON_GreatPerson] Great People patronage cost -50% [ICON_Gold] Gold."),

    ("LOC_GOSSIP_SOURCE_NAT_AIRPORT",                         "Stewardesses at the International Airport learn that "),
    ("LOC_VIZSOURCE_NAT_AIRPORT",                             "The International Airport is complete"),
    ("LOC_VIZSOURCE_ACTION_NAT_AIRPORT",                      "Construct the International Airport"),

