    ("LOC_NAT_WON_CL_AIRPORT_DESCRIPTION",                    "National Wonder. Can only be built once in your empire. Must be built on flat terrain.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]{LOC_HD_NAT_AIRPORT_CORP_ADD}+3 [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Route capacity. Plantations and Lumber Mills in Cities with Airport districts and/or the International Airport wonder provide +50% [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. International [ICON_TradeRoute] Trade Routes to or from this City provide you with Specialty Districts yields as if this City is the destination; this bonus is doubled if the City has an Airport district and/or the International Airport wonder. Provides an additional level of [ICON_VISLIMITED] Diplomatic Visibility to all Civilizations."),
